title: Eps. 137 - What The Hail Is Going On ?
description:
How many of you out there are going after your dream and are flat out frustrated ? You’re doing the work and planting the seeds but you can’t see the crops. This week the guys talk about how hard it is to keep going when you have a dream but aren’t seeing the results. ET talks about how he fought through the hard days but ultimately he never doubted himself and the path he was on. What do you do when you get frustrated ? What do you do when you aren’t seeing the results ? Grab your pen and pad and listen to what ET did during his hard days.
 Time Stamped Topics:
  [09:16] - Fair or Foul
 [16:06] - Right or Wrong
 [26:39] - ET & The NBA
 [45:05] - How To Keep Going
 [53:26] - Quality of Grind
 [1:09:00] - Naivety & Faith
 [1:17:37] - Ask ET
 [1:32:30] - Nugget of The Day
  Listener Perks:
  Organifi is giving our listeners 20% off of their order just go to www.organifi.com/success. Their superfood green juice powder allows you to get your greens anytime anywhere while on the go.
  The Secrets to Success:
  Sometimes it's not what you say it’s how you say it that’s more important than the information that’s being given.
 If you’re not leading then that means you’re being led.
 If you don’t have a plan for your life somebody got one for you.
 The grind has to come before the money.
